
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 08 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mass clavicle' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' box is enabled and automatically selected
And 'I know' box is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and automatically selected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

When I select 'I know' box
And I am on 'Characterization I' tab
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'Well-defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Ill-defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Brush-shaped' radio button is enabled
And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

And 'Intact' radio button is enabled
And 'Destruction' radio button is enabled
And 'Thinning ("scalopping")' radio button is enabled
And 'Permeation' radio button is enabled
And 'Thickening' radio button is enabled

And 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Oval' radio button is enabled
And 'Irregular' radio button is enabled

And 'Fat isodense (approx. -100 HU)' radio button is enabled
And 'Liquid isodense (> 0 HU)' radio button is enabled
And 'Soft tissue isodense' radio button is enabled

And 'Osseous' radio button is enabled
And 'Chondroid' radio button is enabled

When I enter any value between 1 and 150 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter any value between 1 and 150 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled
